msg.term_of_use_before.defaults: Before you use this referral form, please read the text below.

msg.term_of_use_by_using.defaults: By using this form, you agree to these statements:

msg.term_of_use_not_emergency.defaults: PRISM-AOM is not an emergency service.

msg.term_of_use_if_crisis.defaults: If you are in a crisis, please call 9-1-1 or contact one of the services listed on the right side of this page.

msg.term_of_use_wrongly.defaults: You will not use the form wrongly (e.g., spamming or writing false information).

msg.term_of_use_hate.defaults: You will not use the form to spread any hate speech (i.e., speech that is intended to insult, offend, or bully a person).

msg.term_of_use_information_name.defaults: Information without your name will be used to evaluate and improve this referral service.

msg.term_of_use_know_more.defaults: if you would like to know more about the PRISM-AOM project and our Privacy Policy.

msg.term_of_use_under_14.defaults: If you are under 14, the youth mental health team will need to contact your parent(s)/guardian(s) (except in rare situations).

msg.term_of_use_agree_terms.defaults: I have read, understood, and agree to these Terms of Use.

msg.popup_terms.defaults: Please click the box above to indicate that you have read, understand, and agree to these Terms of Use before you can continue.
